cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.IR 

The paper discusses user profiling scenarios around mobile HTTP(S) traffic, which involves security and privacy concerns (cs.CR). It also focuses on personalized services and data-driven user models (cs.SI), as well as personal data rights (cs.CY). The study attempts to model user traits and interests, including demographics and shopping interests (cs.HC), and uses real user data collected in the wild (cs.IR).
